snippet.title: Food And Nutrition Management - Savvy Diner Challenge with Amber and Emma
snippet.description:
The Savvy Diner Challenge - an event by Toronto Public Health in collaboration with Humber College. With multiple colleges involved and students from various programs participating, future chefs create entrees for healthy eating. Humber Food and Nutrition Management students Amber and Emma share their experience in the competition. Find out more about Humber's Food and Nutrition Management diploma program at:
https://healthsciences.humber.ca/programs/food-nutrition-management.html
Initial upload date Dec 12, 2016
